.580" end="34.883">day</span> <span begin="34.883" end="35.092">while</span> <span begin="35.092" end="35.639">slaves</span> <span begin="35.639" end="35.811">were</span> <span begin="35.811" end="36.186">being</span> <span begin="36.186" end="36.757">slaughtered</span> <span begin="36.757" end="36.972">and</span> <span begin="36.972" end="37.448">carted</span> <span begin="37.448" end="38.048">away</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">日日都有奴隶惨死 被运往他处</span></p><p begin="38.055" end="41.273" itunes:key="L11" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="38.055" end="38.618">Across</span> <span begin="38.618" end="38.844">the</span> <span begin="38.844" end="39.308">waves,</span> <span begin="39.308" end="39.427">he</span> <span begin="39.427" end="40.046">struggled</span> <span begin="40.046" end="40.147">and</span> <span begin="40.147" end="40.289">kept</span> <span begin="40.289" end="40.516">his</span> <span begin="40.516" end="40.813">guard</span> <span begin="40.813" end="41.273">up</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">穿越汹涌波涛 他挣扎求生 小心谨慎</span></p><p begin="41.288" end="44.843" itunes:key="L12" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="41.288" end="42.059">Inside,</span> <span begin="42.059" end="42.255">he</span> <span begin="42.255" end="42.499">was</span> <span begin="42.499" end="42.975">longing</span> <span begin="42.975" end="43.100">for</span> <span begin="43.100" end="43.683">something</span> <span begin="43.683" end="43.921">to</span> <span begin="43.921" end="44.171">be</span> <span begin="44.171" end="44.385">a</span> <span begin="44.385" end="44.528">part</span> <span begin="44.528" end="44.843">of</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">在内心深处 他渴望融入某个群体</span></p><p begin="44.853" end="48.669" itunes:key="L13" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="44.853" end="45.059">The</span> <span begin="45.059" end="45.541">brother</span> <span begin="45.541" end="45.744">was</span> <span begin="45.744" end="46.144">ready</span> <span begin="46.144" end="46.475">to</span> <span begin="46.475" end="46.875">beg,</span> <span begin="46.875" end="47.427">steal,</span> <span begin="47.427" end="47.893">borrow,</span> <span begin="47.893" end="48.125">or</span> <span begin="48.125" end="48.669">barter</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">这位仁兄已经准备好去乞讨 偷窃 借贷或交易</span></p><p begin="48.820" end="52.374" itunes:key="L14" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="48.820" end="48.985">Then</span> <span begin="48.985" end="49.153">a</span> <span begin="49.153" end="49.985">hurricane</span> <span begin="49.985" end="50.436">came</span> <span begin="50.436" end="50.886">and</span> <span begin="50.886" end="51.868">devastation</span> <span begin="51.868" end="52.374">reigned</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">然后飓风来袭 毁灭就这样降临</span></p><p begin="52.384" end="56.135" itunes:key="L15" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="52.384" end="52.738">Our</span> <span begin="52.738" end="53.306">man</span> <span begin="53.306" end="53.455">saw</span> <span begin="53.455" end="53.706">his</span> <span begin="53.706" end="54.221">future</span> <span begin="54.221" end="54.655">drip,</span> <span begin="54.655" end="55.138">dripping</span> <span begin="55.138" end="55.389">down</span> <span begin="55.389" end="55.621">the</span> <span begin="55.621" end="56.135">drain</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我们的主人公眼睁睁看着前途一点一点被冲毁</span></p><p begin="56.375" end="1:00.008" itunes:key="L16" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="56.375" end="56.475">Put</span> <span begin="56.475" end="56.575">a</span> <span begin="56.575" end="56.997">pencil</span> <span begin="56.997" end="57.259">to</span> <span begin="57.259" end="57.485">his</span> <span begin="57.485" end="57.979">temple,</span> <span begin="57.979" end="58.717">connected</span> <span begin="58.717" end="58.949">it</span> <span begin="58.949" end="59.192">to</span> <span begin="59.192" end="59.436">his</span> <span begin="59.436" end="1:00.008">brain</span><span ttm:role="x-translati